        <did>
          <unittitle>Series 4: Personal </unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>This series contains Shortall's personal writings, as well as correspondence and newspaper reviews relating to Shortall’s career as a composer.  The correspondence folder also includes the collection’s only photograph of Shortall.   The journals include Shortall’s copies of essays and articles on history, music, psychology, theater, and politics, as well as his reflections on these subjects.  This series contains material from 1937-1984.</p>
